Package: openra
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${cli:Depends},
         libasound2,
         libopenal1,
         libsdl2-2.0-0,
         xdg-utils,
         zenity,
         ttf-freefont,
         ttf-openra (= ${source:Version})
Description: Open-source implementation of the Red Alert engine
 OpenRA is a Libre/Free Real Time Strategy game engine
 supporting early Westwood games like Command & Conquer
 and Command & Conquer: Red Alert and Dune 2000.
 .
 Distributed mods include a reimagining and updating of
 both the Red Alert and Command & Conquer multiplayer games.

Package: ttf-openra
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Open-source implementation of the Red Alert engine (fonts)
 OpenRA is a Libre/Free Real Time Strategy game engine
 supporting early Westwood games like Command & Conquer
 and Command & Conquer: Red Alert and Dune 2000.
 .
 Distributed mods include a reimagining and updating of
 both the Red Alert and Command & Conquer multiplayer games.
 .
 (This package contains the fonts).
